I am having trouble finding the Kickoff Kit of parts CAD models for this season. In years past we usually had access to a zip file with all of the parts included in the kickoff kits. When I say all that might be an exaggeration, but it included most parts I feel like. I found some student experience link mentioned in a solidworks videos but we use fusion 360 and I donâ€™t have a solidworks account. How can I get the CAD bundle for stuff in the black competition tote teams got this season? Maybe my memory is fuzzy but I recall the rookie kit and other tote kits having models sometimes too. This was a nice way to get a starting FRC cad catalog together. If not why not? And is there a good community report for Frc cad models that we all use like the roborio, CTRE parts, etc?
